//Problem Statement:
//Create a class MathUtils with the following methods:
//ï‚· int add(int a, int b)
//ï‚· int multiply(int a, int b)
//ï‚· boolean isEven(int number)
//Write a test class using:
//ï‚· @BeforeEach and @AfterEach to log setup and teardown (i.e start and stop)
//ï‚· @DisplayName for custom test method names
//ï‚· Use @ParameterizedTest with @ValueSource to test isEven() for multiple values